Nubwo Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19) ari indwara nshya, ubumenyi bwacu n'ubumenyi bwacu bugiye buzamuka buhoro buhoro, bishingiye ku bushakashatsi bubera ku bushakashatsi bukorwa no ku by'ubuvuzi; bityo rero, ingamba zo gupima no kuvura na zo zikomeje kuvugururwa.
Muri iyi baruwa, twashubije ku mabwiriza yacu, dushyiraho amahame ya vuba aha yo gusuzuma "ibimenyetso by'ibimenyetso by'uburwayi" n'ibimenyetso by'ibimenyetso by'ibimenyetso by'ibimenyetso by'uburwayi (Icyemezo cya karindwi) nk'uko bigaragara mu mabwiriza ya vuba aha yo gupima no kuvura COVID-19 yashyizwe ahagaragara n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu gishinzwe Ubuzima cya Repubulika ya Chine.
Mu kwezi kwa cumi na kabiri 2019, habayeho icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (2019-nCoV), ubu cyiswe officiellement Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19) n'icyiswe SARS-CoV-2 (Syndrome respiratoire respiratoire actif).
