Bangladesh imaze guhitana abantu bashya batanu bavuye kuri COVID-19, ku gipimo cyo hejuru cyane cy'umunsi umwe
Ku munsi w'ejo, Bangladesh yongeyeho abantu batanu bahitanywe na COVID-19 bapfuye.
Ni umubare munini w'abapfa ku munsi umwe bahitanywe n'iyi virusi.
Kugeza ejo, ibipimo by'abanduye byanditswe n'Ikigo cya Bangladesh cyo kugenzura indwara n'ubushakashatsi (IEDCR) byatangaje ko harimo abanduye 114 n'abantu 33 bakize indwara bari mu rugo.
Kugeza ubu hamaze kuboneka abantu 17 bapfuye.
Mu kiganiro cyabaye kuri interineti, Dr Mirzazi Sabrina Flora, umuyobozi wa IEDCR, yavuze ko hapfuye abagabo bane n'umugore umwe.
