Mu mpera za Mutarama, Leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije gahunda yo guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi, yitwa "intambara y'abaturage" na Xi Jinping, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti ryo mu Bushinwa.
