Uburyo bwo gupima bwari bukubiyemo gutanga amakuru y'ibanze ku bimenyetso binyuze mu bashya baje ku isi binyuze mu porogaramu za telefoni, gupima virusi byihuse ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu 20,000 ku munsi.
