Mu ngamba za mbere leta yatangaje harimo gufunga ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, imikino, no gusenga ku wa Gatanu, no gufunga kaminuza, ibigo by'uburezi bukuru n'amashuri.
Irani yatanze miliyari eshanu z'amadolari y'amanyamerika mu kurwanya iyi virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani, ku wa 26 Gashyantare 2020, yavuze ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato imijyi yahuye n'iki cyorezo, ko abantu bonyine ari bo bazajya mu kato.
Gahunda yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi yatangaje mu kwezi kwa gatatu, nubwo ingendo nyinshi hagati y'imijyi zakomeje mbere y'umwaka mushya wa Peresi Navroz.
Ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe 2020, ahantu ho gusengera aba Shia mu mujyi wa Como harahariwe abapadiri. Mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare, Irani yabaye icyicaro cy'indwara nyuma y'u Bushinwa.
Mu gihe hari ibirego byo guhisha umubare w'ibyago byabaye muri Irani, ibihugu birenga icumi byabonye ko ibyago byabyo byari bifitanye isano na Irani kugeza ku wa 28 Gashyantare, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko ibyago bishobora kuba bikomeye kurusha ibyago 388 byanditswe na Leta ya Irani kugeza icyo gihe.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe ubwo 23 mu banyamuryango bayo 290 bagaragaye ko banduye virusi.
Ku itariki ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani kurekura abantu bose bafunzwe bazira imyigaragambyo y'amahoro, kandi igaha impapuro z'ibanze abanyururu bose bakwiriye kurekurwa.
