Mu mirimo irimo ibyago byo guhura n'abantu benshi harimo gutanga serivisi z'ubuzima, gufasha, gukora mu mavuriro no gutwara abantu bagendana COVID-19 bakekwaho cyangwa bazi ko bafite COVID-19.
Iyo abantu bagaragaje ko bafite ibipimo by'ubwonko, bashobora kuba bafite ibyago byinshi byo guhura n'abantu bafite ubwonko, cyangwa se bakagaragaza ko bafite ubwonko.
Imikorere ikora Aerosol irimo guterwa mu mazuru, guterwa mu mazuru, gushyirwa mu gikombe, gushyirwa mu nda, gukora ibizamini n'imikorere y'amenyo, cyangwa gufata ibipimo by'amabuye y'agaciro.
Ibikorwa byo mu nzu y'abapfuye bafite ibyago byo guhura n'abantu benshi birimo abantu bategura imibiri y'abantu bari bazi cyangwa bakeka ko banduye COVID-19 igihe bapfuye; iyo bagerageje imibiri, baba bafite ibyago byo guhura n'abantu benshi cyane. Ibindi byemezo by'ubuhanga ku mitwe y'aba bantu bafite ibyago birimo icyumba cyo kwiherera abantu bazi cyangwa bakeka COVID-19 mu gihe bakora ibikorwa by'ubuvuzi, harimo no gukora ingufu za Aerosol.
Mu byiciro bimwe by'ubuvuzi no mu miryango, guhangana n'ibiza bishobora kuba byiza.
Ibipimo bigomba gufatwa neza cyane ku rwego rwo kwirinda ubwonko 3.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) rigira inama y'uko abarwayi bazaza, bagashyirwa mu duce twitaruye twitaruye, hagendewe ku niba ari icyorezo cya COVID-19, uretse izindi PPE, OSHA itera inkunga ko abantu bakora mu myanya y'ubuhumekero munsi y'ibirenge 6 by'abarwayi bazi ko banduye SARS-CoV-2, n'abakora ingendo zitera Aerosol.
Muri Amerika, ibikoresho byo guhumeka by'umurongo wa N95 bihanaguye cyangwa birenze byemewe na NIOSH, bigomba gukoreshwa mu rwego rw'ingengabihe yuzuye, yanditse y'ubudahangarwa bw'ubuhumekero, harimo gupima imiterere, imyitozo n'ubuvuzi.
Ibindi bikoresho byo guhumeka bishobora gutanga umutekano mwinshi no kunoza imimerere y'umukozi. WHO ntishyigikira covid-19, kuko COVID-19 ari indwara yo guhumeka aho kwandura binyuze mu mazi.
OMS itera inkunga abasirikare ba Gereza kugenzura gusa ko bagomba gukoresha agapfukamunwa.
Ku bantu barimo gukusanya, kwita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bafite uburyo bwo guhumeka, cyangwa kubaremerera gutwara, badafite ingufu za Aerosol, WHO itera inkunga ko bagira agapfukamunwa, inshyimbo y'amaso, ingofero n'amaboko.
Iyo habayeho igikorwa cyo gukora aerosol, mask ya kirururu isimbuzwa n'umuyoboro wo guhumeka wa N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Kubera ko ku isi hose hari ibikoresho bidahagije by'imiti, OMS ivuga ko imiti ya Telemedicine, uburyo bwo kwirinda inzitizi nk'amadirishya y'ibanze, uburyo bwo kwemerera gusa abafite uburwayi bwa COVID-19 kwinjira mu cyumba kimwe, gukoresha gusa ibikoresho by'imiti bikenewe mu gikorwa runaka, gukoresha uburyo bwo guhumeka bumwe, ku buryo bidashobora gukurwaho mu gihe cy'imibonano y'abarwayi benshi bafite indwara imwe, kugenzura no guhuza inganda z'imiti y'imiti, no guhagarika gukoresha udupfukamunwa ku bantu bafite uburwayi.
