Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku buryo bwemewe n'amategeko n'ubuvanganzo bwakozwe ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012 bwagaragaje ko "gukoresha ACE inhibitors byahuye n'umubare munini w'abantu bafite ibyago byo kurwara indwara ya nimoniya, ku kigero cya 34% ugereranyije n'abafite ubwandu".
Ikindi kandi, "abarwayi bavurwa n'abakize ACE na bo bari bafite ibyago byo kurwara indwara ya pneumonia byagabanutse cyane cyane mu bantu bafite ibyago byo kurwara indwara ya pneumonia, cyane cyane abafite ibyago byo kwicwa n'ibikomere by'umutima n'umutima".
Gukoresha ACE inhibitors byanafitanye isano no kugabanya umubare w'abapfa bapfa bazize indwara ya pneumonia, nubwo ingaruka zari nke cyane ugereranyije n'ibyago by'iyo ndwara yose".
Igitekerezo cy'uko umuntu yahindura umuti wa ACE2 (rhACE2) ari umuti mushya wo kurwara ibihaha, kandi cyerekeranye no kunoza ihumure ry'ibihaha n'ihumure ry'umwuka mu bana b'ingurube bafite ikibazo cy'ihumure ry'ubuhumekero (Lipopolysaccharide-induced acute respiratory distress syndrome).
Mu bantu, rhACE2 ifite ubuzima bw'ikirenga bw'amasaha 10, naho mu gihe cy'amasaha 24 ikora, igatangira gukora mu minota 30.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti uhebuje ku bantu bafite ubukana bw'ibishushanyo bifasha kurwanya ingofero z'umubiri (RAS inhibitors) cyangwa indwara zifasha mu kongera ingofero z'umubiri (angiotensin II).
